And I'm all alone.

263
00:14:37,126 --> 00:14:41,005
No, you're not. You have me, Janet.
I can help you.

264
00:14:41,088 --> 00:14:44,925
It's too hard to explain, but there are
certain aspects of my plan

265
00:14:45,009 --> 00:14:47,094
that you just can't understand.

266
00:14:47,803 --> 00:14:49,847
