but I'm happy you're happy!

280
00:15:37,645 --> 00:15:38,646
Michael?

281
00:15:39,605 --> 00:15:43,317
Hmm? Sorry. Yeah, yes, sorry.

282
00:15:47,196 --> 00:15:48,489
Oh...

283
00:15:49,323 --> 00:15:51,075
