-Come on, dude.

284
00:15:51,158 --> 00:15:54,703
It's dangerous, is what it is.
Vicky could find out!

285
00:15:54,787 --> 00:15:56,830
Then the plan, the whole plan...

286
00:15:56,914 --> 00:16:00,125
