That's the reason.

287
00:16:00,209 --> 00:16:01,460
I don't understand.

288
00:16:01,543 --> 00:16:04,630
Given the situation, it's far safer
to initiate the self-destruct.

289
00:16:04,713 --> 00:16:06,382
Mmm-hmm.

290
00:16:08,592 --> 00:16:10,469
Okay, look, see, here...

291
00:16:10,552 --> 00:16:13,555
Here's the reason.
I promised the four humans

292
00:16:13,639 --> 00:16:16,266
that we would escape to
the Good Place once and for all,

293
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:20,104
and without you, we stand zero chance
of ever making it there.

294
00:16:20,187 --> 00:16:21,730
The new Janet will be able
to help you with that.

295
00:16:21,814 --> 00:16:23,273
But it's not only that, though.

296
00:16:23,357 --> 00:16:27,736
See, it's also because of...
What if Vicky found out?

297
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:29,279
You already asked me that.

298
00:16:29,363 --> 00:16:31,949
Why are you making such a big deal
about turning me into a marble forever?

299
00:16:32,032 --> 00:16:34,910
Because of reasons. There are reasons!

300
00:16:34,994 --> 00:16:38,122
They exist and I don't want
to explain them right now!

301
00:16:38,205 --> 00:16:40,624
-What are the reasons?
-There are reasons!

302
00:16:40,708 --> 00:16:43,627
-But what are they?
-The reason is friends!

303
00:16:50,592 --> 00:16:54,221
You're my friend, Janet.
That's why I can't kill you.

304
00:16:54,847 --> 00:16:57,016
We have been through so much together.

305
00:16:57,099 --> 00:17:00,227
I mean, yeah, sure, for you,
each time I rebooted you,

306
00:17:00,310 --> 00:17:02,104
you met me all over again.

307
00:17:02,187 --> 00:17:06,650
But for me, our relationship
has become important.

308
00:17:07,484 --> 00:17:13,282
You're my oldest, my truest,
my most loyal friend.

309
00:17:13,365 --> 00:17:15,409
I can't just get rid of you

310
00:17:15,492 --> 00:17:19,663
and replace you with some other Janet
I don't even know.

311
00:17:28,714 --> 00:17:31,341
Well, well, well...

312
00:17:31,425 --> 00:17:33,093
Don't do that. Just lay off.

313
00:17:33,177 --> 00:17:34,553
Michael!

314
00:17:36,388 --> 00:17:39,725
That was so nice of you.
I'm glad you said that.

315
00:17:39,808 --> 00:17:42,519
Well, I mean it.

316
00:17:43,187 --> 00:17:46,440
Look at us, a couple of old pals,

317
00:17:46,523 --> 00:17:50,402
