in this crazy world that I built.

318
00:17:50,486 --> 00:17:52,279
Two peas in a pod.

319
00:17:52,362 --> 00:17:55,699
One of whom needs to kill
the other one immediately.

320
00:17:58,243 --> 00:18:00,871
Michael, come on. Kill me!

321
00:18:03,457 --> 00:18:05,501
No, there has to be another way.

322
00:18:05,584 --> 00:18:08,545
This problem you're facing,
