And yeah, it sucks, but trust me,
it's not worth all this drama.

340
00:18:56,260 --> 00:18:58,679
You need to get drunk and go dancing.

341
00:18:58,762 --> 00:19:01,306
You'll forget all about Jason.
Can you get drunk?

342
00:19:01,390 --> 00:19:04,726
