are pretty limited. What about Michael?

349
00:19:22,786 --> 00:19:25,497
-Extraordinarily bad idea.
-Right. Forget it.

350
00:19:25,581 --> 00:19:28,041
But you don't need to worry.

351
00:19:28,125 --> 00:19:29,209
You're awesome.

352
00:19:29,293 --> 00:19:31,545
You contain all the knowledge
in the universe,

353
00:19:31,628 --> 00:19:35,299
