around Jason and Tahani.

362
00:19:53,275 --> 00:19:55,277
[sighs] Thank you for your help.

363
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:58,280
-I'm so glad we're friends.
-Me, too.

364
00:19:58,363 --> 00:20:01,033
