00:20:16,798 --> 00:20:18,467
-Hi, there.
-Hello!

372
00:20:20,052 --> 00:20:22,971
-Janet, who's that man?
-This is my new rebound boyfriend, Derek.

373
00:20:23,055 --> 00:20:26,433
