-[chuckles] Hi, I'm Derek.

374
00:20:26,516 --> 00:20:27,601
You must be--

375
00:20:27,684 --> 00:20:31,396
Oh... Okay, that makes more sense.

376
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,689
You must be Michael.

377
00:20:32,773 --> 00:20:34,983
Janet's made a lot of talk-talk
into my earholes about you.

378
00:20:35,067 --> 00:20:37,861
Michael, Michael, Klichael, Klichael.

379
00:20:37,945 --> 00:20:40,030
Janet, you can't make a person.

380
00:20:40,113 --> 00:20:41,740
I know. But I did, though.

381
00:20:41,823 --> 00:20:45,494
Eleanor said that to forget about Jason,
I should create a rebound guy.

382
00:20:45,577 --> 00:20:47,037
