383
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,373
-I'm her boyfriend and she made me.
-He's so nice.

384
00:20:49,456 --> 00:20:53,210
[laughs] Whoa! Look at this glass.
Oh, my God.

385
00:20:54,169 --> 00:20:57,047
