What's going on right now?

386
00:20:57,130 --> 00:21:00,008
{\an8}It's my first time making someone,
so he might be a bit off.

387
00:21:00,092 --> 00:21:02,261
{\an8}This could be...
Please put that down.

388
00:21:02,344 --> 00:21:05,889
{\an8}This could be very dangerous!
