391
00:21:12,020 --> 00:21:13,230
{\an8}Can you believe this?

392
00:21:13,313 --> 00:21:15,482
{\an8}-Derek, is it Derek?
-It's Derek.

393
00:21:15,565 --> 00:21:18,402
{\an8}Derek, could you please give me and Janet
a moment alone?

394
00:21:18,485 --> 00:21:20,070
{\an8}Go back to the void.
I'll be there in a minute.

395
00:21:20,153 --> 00:21:21,989
{\an8}-Okay, I'll miss you like crazy.
-I'll miss you more.

396
00:21:22,072 --> 00:21:24,783
{\an8}No, I'll miss you more. Bye!

397
00:21:24,866 --> 00:21:27,286
[chuckling] What a dork, am I right?
